<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="role-n">role <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /rəʊl/    美 /roʊl/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>角色：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the <strong>leading role</strong> 
主角</p></div>

<h3 id="play-the-role-of">play the role of</h3>
<p>1.<strong>扮演…的角色：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He played the role of a successful lawyer in the play.
他在剧中扮演一位成功的律师。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>作用：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a <strong>leading role</strong> 
重要作用</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="play-an-role-in">play a(n) … role in</h3>
<p>1.<strong>在…中起…作用：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Farming plays an important role in the country’s economy. 
农业在该国经济中起着重要的作用。</p></div></div>